branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
D-sub connector for Series VQ1000/2000 solenoid valves. The D-sub connector reduces installation labor for electrical connections. Using the D-sub connector (25P), (15P as semi-standard) conforming to MIL standard gives a wide interchangeability. A top or side receptacle position can be selected in accordance with the available mounting space. Support a maximum of 24 stations.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduces installation labor for electrical connections
&lt;li&gt;Top or side receptacle position for space limitations
&lt;li&gt;Supports up to 24 stations
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The back pressure check valve prevents cylinder malfunction caused by other valve exhaust. It is effective when a single action cylinder is used, or an exhaust center type solenoid valve is used. Compatible with series VQ1000/2000 Base Mounted Plug-in Units.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For series VQ1000/2000 Base Mounted Plug-in Units
&lt;li&gt;Prevents cylinder malfunction caused by valve exhaust
&lt;li&gt;Effective when single action cylinders or exhaust center type solenoid valves are used
&lt;li&gt;2 pcs. 
